						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the compound of <hi rend="italic">Liṅgāyata-maṭha.</hi></p>						

						<p>Circa 17th century.</p>						

						<p>It is registers a gift of the village Vīrasamudra in the <hi rend="italic">vaḷita of</hi> Chadumu to god Mallikārjunadēva by <hi rend="italic">daḷavāvi</hi> Virēgauḍa of Anekal, with the permission of Chikkarāya-Tammegauḍa of Suguṭūru.</p>						

						<p>It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Rākshasa Āśvija śu. 10.</hi> The date cannot be verified for want of further details.</p>						

						</summary>
